              "id": "afaae257",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2>Long-Term\u00a0&amp;\u00a0Recurring Commercial Floor Care Programs</h2><p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"326\">Keeping your facility\u2019s floors in top condition isn\u2019t a one-time job; it\u2019s an ongoing commitment to safety, cleanliness, and brand image.</p><p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"326\">With Midland Floor Care\u2019s Long-Term &amp; Recurring Service Programs, you get consistent, professional maintenance that protects your investment and keeps your space looking its best all year.</p><p data-start=\"328\" data-end=\"495\">We partner with facility managers, property owners, and operations teams to build custom floor care schedules that match your traffic patterns, budget, and operations.</p><p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"539\"><strong data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"539\">Why choose a recurring service program</strong></p><ul data-start=\"540\" data-end=\"914\"><li data-start=\"540\" data-end=\"623\"><p data-start=\"542\" data-end=\"623\">Preserve your flooring investment: prevent premature wear and costly replacements</p></li><li data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"694\"><p data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"694\">Consistent brand image: floors stay clean, polished, and guest-ready</p></li><li data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"775\"><p data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"775\">Operational efficiency: scheduled maintenance reduces emergencies and downtime</p></li><li data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"832\"><p data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"832\">Budget control: predictable costs and planned services</p></li><li data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"914\"><p data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"914\">Health and safety: regular cleaning reduces slip risks and improves air quality</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"991\"><strong data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"935\">What\u2019s included:</strong></p><p data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"991\">Your plan is customized, but common components include:</p><ul data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1357\"><li data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1063\"><p data-start=\"994\" data-end=\"1063\">Commercial carpet cleaning: scheduled deep cleans and spot treatments</p></li><li data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1131\"><p data-start=\"1066\" data-end=\"1131\">Tile and grout maintenance: routine cleaning and periodic sealing</p></li><li data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1217\"><p data-start=\"1134\" data-end=\"1217\">Hard surface restoration and polishing: ongoing care for stone, vinyl, and concrete</p></li><li data-start=\"1218\" data-end=\"1285\"><p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1285\">Protective coating applications: maintain shine and resist damage</p></li><li data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1357\"><p data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1357\">High-traffic focus: targeted care for entries, corridors, and lobbies</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1384\"><strong data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1384\">Industries we support</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1385\" data-end=\"1533\"><li data-start=\"1385\" data-end=\"1404\"><p data-start=\"1387\" data-end=\"1404\">Corporate offices</p></li><li data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1429\"><p data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1429\">Hotels and hospitality</p></li><li data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1459\"><p data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1459\">Retail and shopping centers</p></li><li data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1483\"><p data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1483\">Healthcare facilities</p></li><li data-start=\"1484\" data-end=\"1510\"><p data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1510\">Educational institutions</p></li><li data-start=\"1511\" data-end=\"1533\"><p data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"1533\">Government buildings</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1551\"><strong data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1551\">How it works</strong></p><ol data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1827\"><li data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1625\"><p data-start=\"1555\" data-end=\"1625\">Facility walkthrough: assess flooring types, conditions, and traffic</p></li><li data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1691\"><p data-start=\"1629\" data-end=\"1691\">Custom service plan: built around your operations and budget</p></li><li data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1756\"><p data-start=\"1695\" data-end=\"1756\">Scheduled maintenance: monthly, quarterly, or annual cycles</p></li><li data-start=\"1757\" data-end=\"1827\"><p data-start=\"1760\" data-end=\"1827\">Ongoing communication: reports and check-ins to ensure satisfaction</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"1829\" data-end=\"1878\"><strong data-start=\"1829\" data-end=\"1878\">Why partner with Midland Floor Care long term</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1879\" data-end=\"2126\"><li data-start=\"1879\" data-end=\"1931\"><p data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"1931\">Dedicated account management: one point of contact</p></li><li data-start=\"1932\" data-end=\"1991\"><p data-start=\"1934\" data-end=\"1991\">Flexible scheduling: nights, weekends, and off-peak hours</p></li><li data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2065\"><p data-start=\"1994\" data-end=\"2065\">Proven ROI: longer floor life, fewer replacements, fewer urgent repairs</p></li><li data-start=\"2066\" data-end=\"2126\"><p data-start=\"2068\" data-end=\"2126\">The Midland Shine Standard: results guaranteed every visit</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2128\" data-end=\"2315\"><strong data-start=\"2128\" data-end=\"2162\">CTA: Schedule an on-site visit</strong><br />Ready to set up your program? <a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule an on-site visit today.</a> Call us or request a visit online and we\u2019ll build your plan around your facility\u2019s needs.</p><p data-start=\"2317\" data-end=\"2474\">Floor care is not a project; it\u2019s a program. Let Midland Floor Care be your trusted partner in maintaining a clean, safe, professional facility year-round.</p><p data-start=\"2476\" data-end=\"2486\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you.</p><ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/the-top-methods-for-cost-effective-floor-maintenance/\">The Top Methods for Cost-Effective Floor Maintenance</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li>\n</ul><div style=\"background:#F3FCF4;border-left:4px solid #43A94B;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;border-radius:6px\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0F1411\">Related Services</p><ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.9\"><li><a href=\"/customized-commercial-floor-care-solutions/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Customized Commercial Floor Care Solutions</a></li><li><a href=\"/janitorial-housekeeping-facility-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Janitorial & Housekeeping Facility Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-upholstery/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Upholstery</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-tile-grout-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Tile & Grout Cleaning</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-carpet-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Carpet Cleaning Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-hard-surface-floor-restoration/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Hard Surface Floor Restoration</a></li></ul></div>",
                "align": "left",
                "text_color": "#0F1411",
